<episodedetails><title>Inside Animal Minds: Dogs &amp; Super Senses (2)</title><plot>On Inside Animal Minds’ second installment, “Dogs &amp; Super Senses”, see everything from a dog that seems to use smell to tell time to a dolphin that can “see” with its ears, discover how animals use their senses in ways we humans can barely imagine. But it’s not just the senses that are remarkable -- it’s the brains that process them.</plot></episodedetails>